Package org.hms.services.medicalrecord

Class PatientParticulars

java.lang.Object
org.hms.entities.AbstractTableEntry
org.hms.services.medicalrecord.PatientParticulars
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class PatientParticulars extends AbstractTableEntry
The PatientParticulars class represents the details of a patient, including their ID, name, date of birth, gender, and blood type. This class extends the AbstractTableEntry, allowing it to be used as an entry in a table.
